                            <expan>Harb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vogt <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet,
                        daz <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sein habe wider werde. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
